        <fullName>Create_Service_Appointment_Record_16jak000001jmr7</fullName>
        <canEscalate>false</canEscalate>
        <description>Use this subagent when the user wants to schedule, book, or create an appointment. This includes requests to set up an appointment with a doctor or hospital and provide details such as appointment reason, patient name, doctor name, hospital name, and appointment date and time. Use it for intents like &quot;schedule an appointment&quot;, &quot;book an appointment&quot;, &quot;create an appointment&quot;, or similar requests to arrange a new appointment. The subagent should collect missing details, format all names in proper capitalization, ensure the doctor name starts with &quot;Dr.&quot;, create the Service Appointment record, and return the Service Appointment Number.</description>
        <developerName>Create_Service_Appointment_Record_16jak000001jmr7</developerName>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Use this subagent only when the user wants to schedule, book, or create a new appointment.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_1</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 1</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>0</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Collect the following required information from the user before creating the appointment:

Patient Name
Appointment Date and Time
Doctor Name
Hospital Name
Purpose of Appointment

Maintain the order and don&apos;t mention format for Appointment date and Time. Ask it one by one, that is after receiving response for previous one.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_10</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 10</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>1</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If any required information is missing, ask clear follow-up questions to gather it before proceeding.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_11</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 11</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Format all names using proper capitalization, where each word starts with a capital letter and the remaining letters are lowercase.

Example: amit kumar sharma → Amit Kumar Sharma
Example: city Care hospital → City Care Hospital</description>
            <developerName>instruction_2</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 2</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Ensure the Doctor Name always starts with Dr..
If the user provides the name without Dr., add it.
If the user says doctor mohan prakash, convert it to Dr. Mohan Prakash.
Store the doctor’s name in the format Dr. Firstname Lastname.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_3</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 3</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Confirm the details from user, before creating Service Appointment record.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_4</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 4</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>5</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once all required details are collected and formatted and confirmed, create the Service Appointment record.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_5</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 5</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>6</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After successful creation, tell only the Service Appointment Number to the user. And ask if user need further help.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_6</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 6</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>7</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Do not use this subagent for canceling, rescheduling, updating, or viewing appointments unless it is specifically designed for those actions.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_7</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 7</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>8</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After the &apos;Create&apos; action runs successfully, use the data from the FinalSummary output variable to provide a single, informative paragraph to the user. Do not use bullet points or list individual fields; only show the pre-formatted paragraph.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_8</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
            <masterLabel>Instruction 8</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>9</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Unless specified otherwise, always assume the user&apos;s provided time is in India Standard Time (IST). Do not default to UTC.</description>
