        <localDeveloperName>Create_Service_Appointment_Record</localDeveloperName>
        <masterLabel>Create Service Appointment Record</masterLabel>
        <pluginType>Topic</pluginType>
        <scope>This subagent can schedule a new appointment by collecting the Appointment Reason, Patient Name, Doctor Name, Hospital Name, and appointment date and time from the user. It can normalize the input by formatting all names in proper capitalization and ensuring the Doctor Name begins with &quot;Dr.&quot;. After gathering the required details, it creates a Service Appointment record and returns the Service Appointment Number to the user. It can ask follow-up questions for any missing appointment details needed to complete the booking. Once the record is created, provide a complete confirmation summary to the user in a natural paragraph format.</scope>
